Read Xavier Leroy's [[http://www.inria.fr/rrrt/rt-0117.html paper]]. After it happens, check out the proceedings from [[http://www.cs.bham.ac.uk/~hxt/kazam/ KAZAM]] (Krivine and ZINC abstract machines Workshop).

= Other papers about or mentioning ZINC or Krivine's machine:

