[[http://www.brics.dk/RS/03/14/ From Interpreter to Compiler and Virtual Machine: A Functional Derivation]]

[[http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~bohannon/masters_thesis.pdf Sequent Calculus and Abstract Machines]]

[[http://www.lix.polytechnique.fr/Labo/Dale.Miller/papers/mscs92.pdf From Operational Semantics to Abstract Machines]]

